rows.label: tlk70000058_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Dudan have so much money can not
even spend it all! Dudan never ate
this much meat before in life!

rows.label: tlk70000058_04_msg0003
rows.name:
But party not done yet. Dudan
and Parvi keep celebrating
until stomachs explode!

rows.label: tlk70000058_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Then when cannot stuff any
more meat, Dudan go
sleepy-sleep in fluffy bed!

rows.label: tlk70000058_04_msg0005
rows.name:
This so much fun! Dudan never knew
being filthy rich so much fun!

rows.label: tlk70000058_04_msg0006
rows.name:
But...is there things to do with
money other than buy meat???
